00075 int CheckTMEs::ProcessEntry(TGlobalData* gData,const TSetupData *setup){
00076     // Loop over each TME
00077     for(MuonEventList::const_iterator i_tme=gMuonEvents.begin();

00079         // total pulses
00080         fTotalPulses->Fill((*i_tme)->TotalNumPulses());

00082                 i_det!=fDetectors.end(); ++i_det){
00083             // pulses per channel
00084             fPulsesPerDetector->Fill((*i_tme)->NumPulses(*i_det), i_det - fDetectors.begin());
00085         }
00086         // fill flags hist
00087         if((*i_tme)->HasMuonHit()) fFlags->Fill("Muon Hit",1.);
00088         if((*i_tme)->HasMuonPileup()) fFlags->Fill("Muon PileUp",1.);
00089         //if((*i_tme)->WasEarlyInEvent()) fFlags->Fill("Early",1.);
00090         //else if((*i_tme)->WasLateInEvent()) fFlags->Fill("Late",1.);
00091         //else  
00092             fFlags->Fill("Healthy",1.);
00093     }
00094   return 0;
